fields.name: Enabled
fields.description: Whether to enable on kube-proxy on the cluster (if no 'kubeProxyConfig' exists, kube-proxy is enabled in AKS by default without these customizations).

fields.name: IPvsConfig
fields.description: Holds configuration customizations for IPVS. May only be specified if 'mode' is set to 'IPVS'.

fields.name: Mode
fields.description: Specify which proxy mode to use ('IPTABLES' or 'IPVS')
